headline: Airbnb to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: Airbnb, Inc. (NASDAQ: ABNB) today announced that the company's second quarter 2025 financial results will be released after market close on Wednesday, August 6, 2025. The company's shareholder letter will be made available on the Airbnb Investor Relations website at https://investors.airbnb.com.
